title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 7-3.9 - Fire safety
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 7-3.9 - Fire safety

State Regulations

Structures not meeting the definition of a camping unit which are available for overnight transient occupancy, shall meet the fire safety requirements contained in Subpart 7-1 of this Part. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10
